<h2><a href="https://osxdaily.com/2023/11/14/how-to-make-stickers-from-photos-for-messages-on-iphone/" rel="bookmark" title="How to Make Stickers from Photos for Messages on iPhone">How to Make Stickers from Photos for Messages on iPhone</a></h2>
<div id="subhead_block">
<span class="subhead_lefty">Nov 14, 2023 - <a href="https://osxdaily.com/2023/11/14/how-to-make-stickers-from-photos-for-messages-on-iphone/#comments">3 Comments</a></span>
<span class="subhead_righty"></span>
</div>

<div class="contenttext">

<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-610x365.jpg" alt="Stickers in Messages on iPhone" width="610" height="365" class="lazy lazy-hidden aligncenter size-large wp-image-127805" srcset="" data-srcset="https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-610x365.jpg 610w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-300x180.jpg 300w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-768x460.jpg 768w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-1536x919.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-2048x1226.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 610px) 100vw, 610px" /><noscript><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-610x365.jpg" alt="Stickers in Messages on iPhone" width="610" height="365" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-127805" srcset="https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-610x365.jpg 610w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-300x180.jpg 300w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-768x460.jpg 768w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-1536x919.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/stickers-messages-iphone-2048x1226.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 610px) 100vw, 610px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Stickers are a fun and creative way to enhance your iMessage experience, and the latest versions of iOS support a feature that allow you to easily make your own stickers from any of your own photos, right from your iPhone. For example, maybe you have a picture of a great dog or cat, or yourself, that you want to turn into a sticker that you can plaster onto messages. No sweat, you can do that with ease.</p>
